      "text": "7. Bet tee irr to Derribu\npahrkahpuschi ka Ahdams/tur tee\nirr nepeetizzigi prett manni tur-\nrejschees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Gileada irr weens Pils-\ntahts pilns Launadarritaju/ un\nar Askins-Wainahm apmihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Ka tee Laupitaji uhs kah-\ndu Wihru gluhne/ ta irr to\nPreesteru Draudse us to Zettu/\nkur uhs Sikeinu ja-eet/ teescham/\ntee darra negantus Darbus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Es redsu weenu breefini-\ngu Leetu ceftch ta Israëta Nam-\nma: Tur irr Eewräima Mauzi-\nha/ Israëls irr sagahuijees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Tomehr tew Juhda irr\nwehl Plaufchana preefschä/ kad\nees to Zeetumu manno Lauschu\natgreesischu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Un tee ne dohnna farva\nSirdi/ ka es wiſſu winno Lau-\nnunu peeminnu. Bet nu ap-\nmettahs pretti teem winnu Dar-\nbi/ tee irr manna Preefschä.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Tee eepreezina to Kehninu\nar tawu Launumu/ un to Leelu-\nKungu ar jaweem Melkeim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Tee pahrlausa wiſſnotaz\nto Laulibu/ tee irr ka Zeplis/ kas\nkurrinabts tohp no Zeppeja/ kas\nmittejahs nomohdä buht/ kad\nwiſſch to Mihku irr mihzijs/\nkamehr tas irr pahrruhdsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Schi irr muhta Kehnina\nDeena (fakka tee/) tad fahk tee\nLeel-Kungi no Wihna Karstuna\nwahji tapt/ wiſſch feſteept tawu\nRohku pee teem Mehdtajeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Jo tee dohdahs ar jawu\nSirdi/ (fas) ka Zeplis irr / uhs\nWiltibu. Winno Zeppejs gull\nzaur Nakti/ Rihta wiſſch degg\nka leefmains Ugguns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "7. Tee irr wiſſi eekahrfuschi\nka Zeplis/ un eerihj jawus Teet-\nueschus/ wiſſi winno Kehninu\nfriht/ neweens irr starp teem/\nkas manni peefauz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Gewräims janzzahs ar tahm\nTautahm/ Gewräims irr weena\nKarratcha/ ko neweens apgreesch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Sweſchi norihj winna\nSpehku/ un to wiſſch ne noman-\nna/ ir tas Strinums irr pahr\nwinnu nahzis/ un tatschu wiſſch\nne atsihst.\n"
    }
